{
  "stem": "2391.2",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He has his arm around me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I see his, blood-shot eyes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were singing songs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and he grabbed me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I thought, oh, god, what am I going to do?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother and this other woman who was a friend of her, they were being, being chased by some other SS guy.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And all of a sudden, there was this big-- this officer comes in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he looks at her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He says-- and they all stand up to attention.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As drunk as they were, you know, they still had discipline.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They stand to attention.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he says, everybody, everybody up-- everybody go upstairs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they disappear.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in one second, they were gone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he apologized to us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he says, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm sorry that this happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were punished.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I know, I know, he got them because they were out of-- luckily, I mean, he saved us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Who knows what would have happened?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this is your journey back-- on your way back to Antwerp?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the journey back to Antwerp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, we finally made it back to Antwerp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A few days, it was a few days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Strangely enough, that was in May 1940.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was unusual good weather that, that whole month, because there were millions of refugees all over the area.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And people had to sleep outdoors.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, you know, practically live outdoors during that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so that was a great help.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know where he was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know where he was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know if he was alive or not, and where he was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, no communication whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Much, much later, we started hearing from him.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
